{"tid":734431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(法律JJ入) 報咗Wall Street English 課程 想cut","createTime":"2018-07-08T15:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T12:21:07.000Z","uid":150568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c222edab65fe0912b1ebc739277dc0ca22001193","tid":734431,"uid":150568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:19:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的，有啲長同sorly for 1999<br />\n<br />\n我報咗Wall Street English 18個月的課程。<br />\n簽約期間，我當時冇睇清楚條款內容，而分校職員都冇詳細說明條約內容，直接叫我簽名。期後我發現終止課程校方只接受三個原因：一.危疾 二.死亡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  三.永久離港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/224742_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F224742_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=c7125311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後因為我嚟緊會開始讀一個三年既part-time degree，將唔會有空閒上堂，所以就書面申請咗要退學。<br />\n<br />\n兩個禮拜之後終於收到回覆，拒絕咗退學申請，原因係唔符合嗰三個條件。佢地提出三個替代方案：一.報讀其他課程（但我根本沒有時間上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）二.轉移合約俾其他人 （CLS個19合約仲要轉俾人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）三.凍結課程（三年之後再上堂，但期間繼續要扣錢on99 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">消費者及不公平合約條款：法律保障不足及相關改革建議<br />\n</span></strong><a href=\"http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%80%85%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%B9%B3%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E6%A2%9D%E6%AC%BE%EF%BC%9A%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E5%8F%8A%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk-lawyer.org%2Ftc%2Fcontent%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%258F%258A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%25B4%2584%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%25AC%25BE%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%259C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%259D%25A9%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0&d=CJMkycaNPSOu6GMVJ4Fa2y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=513e245e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%80%85%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%B9%B3%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E6%A2%9D%E6%AC%BE%EF%BC%9A%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E5%8F%8A%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n之前睇到有一條《不合情理合約條例》(第458章) ，想知道下一步可以點做。我將會約消委會諮詢一下。<br />\n<br />\nPS: 知道自己簽約on9 插輕力啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba3a37ae9a2efae65c430b3a97c014fa59622b7","tid":734431,"uid":142523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T16:14:23.000Z","msg":"是否符合條件者退學可以拎返哂餘下學費?"},{"pid":"3adfc197748c5e837c8fa05d8724e1e26f08519a","tid":734431,"uid":86854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T01:02:24.000Z","msg":"我都想知道喱個問題！因為我都想退！"},{"pid":"4e8788822447d8413cbc01039f929de94ccda401","tid":734431,"uid":198933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c222edab65fe0912b1ebc739277dc0ca22001193","tid":734431,"uid":150568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:19:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的，有啲長同sorly for 1999<br />\n<br />\n我報咗Wall Street English 18個月的課程。<br />\n簽約期間，我當時冇睇清楚條款內容，而分校職員都冇詳細說明條約內容，直接叫我簽名。期後我發現終止課程校方只接受三個原因：一.危疾 二.死亡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  三.永久離港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/224742_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F224742_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=c7125311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後因為我嚟緊會開始讀一個三年既part-time degree，將唔會有空閒上堂，所以就書面申請咗要退學。<br />\n<br />\n兩個禮拜之後終於收到回覆，拒絕咗退學申請，原因係唔符合嗰三個條件。佢地提出三個替代方案：一.報讀其他課程（但我根本沒有時間上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）二.轉移合約俾其他人 （CLS個19合約仲要轉俾人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）三.凍結課程（三年之後再上堂，但期間繼續要扣錢on99 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">消費者及不公平合約條款：法律保障不足及相關改革建議<br />\n</span></strong><a href=\"http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%80%85%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%B9%B3%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E6%A2%9D%E6%AC%BE%EF%BC%9A%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E5%8F%8A%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk-lawyer.org%2Ftc%2Fcontent%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%258F%258A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%25B4%2584%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%25AC%25BE%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%259C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%259D%25A9%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0&d=CJMkycaNPSOu6GMVJ4Fa2y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=513e245e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%80%85%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%B9%B3%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E6%A2%9D%E6%AC%BE%EF%BC%9A%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E5%8F%8A%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n之前睇到有一條《不合情理合約條例》(第458章) ，想知道下一步可以點做。我將會約消委會諮詢一下。<br />\n<br />\nPS: 知道自己簽約on9 插輕力啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T06:33:10.000Z","msg":"組隊<br />\n退"},{"pid":"49db8e56a0355d9331f006d61c5f4f50cb348044","tid":734431,"uid":337106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:21:07.000Z","msg":"有冇人退到學 我而家退唔到 好撚煩<img src=\"/asset